@node Introduction "JUKI6300: An Introduction"
@{b}Introduction@{ub}
============

 You have an old, big, heavy JUKI6300 daisywheel printer?
 Then you need this new, nice, small printer driver.

 Is there anyone who own a manual for the JUKI6300?
 Please mail me the CommandTable with the ESC-sequences.

@endnode

@node Requirements "JUKI6300: System requirements"
@{b}Requirements@{ub}
============

 What do you need?

     JUKI6300 should work on every Amiga with:

     - a JUKI6300 daisywheel printer

     - OS2.0 or higher

@endnode

@node Install "JUKI6300: Install JUKI6300"
@{b}Install JUKI6300@{ub}
================

 Just copy JUKI6300 to devs:printers,
 start PrinterPrefs, chose JUKI6300,
 click save or use.

@endnode

